msgstr "When ye give the signal, yer user data, Spaces, and Space keys will be synchronized across all yer devices. Be warned, this makes it easier to see when ye've joined new Spaces, but not which ones."

#: src/components/modals/SpaceSettingsModal/General.tsx:281
